Isaiah 56-10 <t><f>ⓡ</f> His watchmen are blind; </t><t>they are all without knowledge; </t><t>they are all silent <f>ⓢ</f>dogs; </t><t>they cannot bark, </t><t>dreaming, lying down, </t><t>loving to slumber.</t>
